Then there's what are called assets at the edges. These are assets that have never been ownable in a fractional form. So the tokenization of a building, the tokenization of a carbon credit, these things are just very difficult to own and gain access to. And because tokenization is a new way to provide ownership of things, these things are being turned into ownership rights through tokenization. Then there's the second really big reason why people do tokenization, or real world asset tokenization, and that's for efficiency purposes.
